name: Portable Clothes Rack
description:
This is perfect for taking to craft shows! Looks way more stylish than on of those flimsy white racks you get at the big box stores and it's sturdier. All Indie Fixtures items are handmade! The rack is galvanized metal pipe and little over 5 feet high. The space for hanging your clothes is about a foot long. The base is a 12" x 28" solid plywood base, not that ugle chip board so you won't be embarrassed to let it show. Very quick to set up. The pole is 5 feet long so it will have to be considered in your travel arrangements and shipping. (I can offer a sectional pole that's longest part is 3 feet, for slightly more.)
Questions welcome! Please use the contact button on the right side of the page. Thanks for shopping with me and please, tell a friend.

name: Rack Signs - Male, Female and Sale
description:
This sign is perfect for directing your customers to the right area of your shop. Handmade, like all my fixtures, it's about 12" high and 2 1/2" wide. It intended to fit pipe racks in 3/4" to 1" diameter. 
I also make Male Rack Signs in a complimentary style and a "Sale" sign with the letters vertical.
Questions welcome! Please use the Contact button on the right side of the page.
Please specify which sign you want when ordering.
Thanks for shopping with me and please, tell a friend.
